					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p158479">Re: How do I do in CA65 things I do in ASM6?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=158479#p158479"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Wed Nov 04, 2015 7:45 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
